name: Pray For Philippines 2
description:
100% Cotton Pre-Shrunk Heavyweight Blue, Red, & Black Tees.

Pray For Philippines prayer hands front print and small version on top back print.

* custom colorways are also available on request. please email specifics after placing order to felgood86@yahoo.com

This is a relief effort for the victims of the recent Typhoon Yolanda/Haiyan and the previous high magnitude earthquake that hit the same region.

100% of the proceeds will be donated to the Oahu Filipino Community Council Foundation of which AARP will match dollar for dollar up to $500,000. OFCCF will be directly donating the monies to an NGO contact in the Philippines to make sure that it reaches the right people and the ones in need. A lesson learned from previous relief efforts. 

*currently taking pre-orders

name: G.W.O.P.O
description:
100% Cotton Pre-Shrunk Heavyweight  CREAM Tees

Front: G.W.O.P.O - Handsomely Rich in money green ink.

Back:  small Felgood Customs logo in money green ink.

The concept to this design is being handsomely rich in a non monetary fashion. Being rich with everything other than money. 

G.W.O.P. is a slang for money and an acronym for George Washington On Paper. Guwapo is Pilipino for handsome. Hence the word G.W.O.P.o.

*taking pre-orders and temporarily in CREAM color only
